Description: 
        # Poio Library
        
        A NLP library of common functionality within the Poio project.
        
        ## Install package
        
        Local install:
        
            $ pip install path/to/poio-lib
        
        Install from PyPI:
        
            $ pip install poio-lib
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```
        import poiolib
        langinfo = poiolib.LangInfo()
        iso_639_1 = langinfo.iso_639_1_for_3("deu")
        ```
        
        ## Running the tests
        
            $ python -m unittest discover
         
        
